{{DEFAULTSORT:Comparison Of Encrypted External Drives}}
[[Category:Disk encryption]]
[[Category:Computing comparisons|Encrypted external drives]]
[[Category:Cryptographic software]]

The following is a comparison of various add-in packages available to do [[Monte Carlo method|Monte Carlo]] probabilistic modeling and risk analysis. Add-ins covered are for [[Microsoft Excel]] on [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]]. 
Mac software and tools for other platforms, such as [[R (programming language)|R]] or [[MATLAB|Matlab]] are not included.

[[Decision-making software]] is reviewed separately.

