== Reporting results ==

{| class="wikitable sortable" style="text-align: center; font-size: 85%; width: 100%; table-layout: fixed;"

|-
! style="width: 12em; text-align: left" | Name
! Includes reporting tool
! Report export formats<ref name="viewer">Exporting file formats to share graphical and statistical results.</ref>
! Save and retrieve results
! Editing of graphs<ref name="edit">Ability to change colour schemes, fonts, add markers and legends, etc.</ref>
! [[Histogram]]
! [[Cumulative frequency analysis|Cumulative]]
! [[Time series]] plot
! Spider<ref name="spider">See, for example: https://www.google.ca/search?q=spider+sensitivity+analysis&tbm=isch&tbo=u&source=univ&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjazfDmvOvJAhVJmR4KHTYJBO4QsAQIIA&biw=1920&bih=906</ref>
