! [[Box plot|Box]]
! [[Summary statistics|Statistics]]
! Simulation data
! Results filtering<ref name="filter">The ability to select a subset of the simulation results (e.g. scenarios that result in a loss) thereby allowing the user to investigate scenarios of greatest interest.</ref>
