{{Infobox book | image = Karta tytułowa Słownika geograficznego Królestwa Polskiego i innych krajów słowiańskich.jpg | image_size = 200px | caption = Title page of the first edition | author = [[Filip Sulimierski]] | country = Poland | language = Polish | genre = [[Dictionary]] | publisher = | pub_date = 1880–1902 | english_pub_date = }} The '''Geographical Dictionary of the Kingdom of Poland and other Slavic Countries''' ({{lang-pl|Słownik geograficzny Królestwa Polskiego i innych krajów słowiańskich}}) is a monumental [[Poland|Polish]] [[gazetteer]], published 1880–1902 in [[Warsaw]] by [[Filip Sulimierski]], [[Bronisław Chlebowski]], [[Władysław Walewski]] and others.
