{{Orphan|date=October 2015}}

'''VfB''' is a [[German language|German]] abbreviation for ''Verein für Bewegungsspiele'' ("Association for Active Games"), used in [[association football]] team names, as in [[VfB Stuttgart]] or [[VfB Leipzig]].

